<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Holy Sheet. You Earned It.</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@700&family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#E8E0D4;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;">

<!--[if !mso]><!-->
<!-- PREVIEW TEXT: Controls inbox snippet. Pad with invisible chars so email client doesn't pull in body text. -->
<div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;">{{ event.cycle_count }} cycles in. Most guys quit. You didn't. Here's your reward.&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;</div>
<!--<![endif]-->

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#E8E0D4;padding:48px 16px;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:580px;width:100%;background:#F5EFE6;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(13,59,35,0.18);">

        <!-- AMBER TOP BAR -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#C4733A;padding:10px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <span style="font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0D3B23;">The Bastard Club</span>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- HEADER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#0D3B23;padding:48px 40px 40px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:700;color:#F5EFE6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;line-height:1;">Holy Sheet.</h1>
            <p style="margin:12px 0 0 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.65);letter-spacing:1px;">You actually did it.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- AMBER DIVIDER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#C4733A;height:3px;font-size:0;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>

        <!-- REWARD HERO -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#0D3B23;padding:40px 40px 48px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:72px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:20px;">{{ event.milestone_emoji }}</div>
            <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#C4733A;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;">{{ event.milestone_name }}</h2>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.65);line-height:1.6;">{{ event.milestone_description }}</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- BODY -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:44px 40px 0 40px;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#0D3B23;line-height:1.5;">{% if person.first_name %}{{ person.first_name }}{% else %}Most guys{% endif %} — most guys cancel after month one.<br>You didn't.</p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;"><strong>{{ event.cycle_count }} subscription cycles.</strong> That's not nothing. That's commitment. And now you're getting paid for it.</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">Your <strong>{{ event.milestone_name }}</strong> is on its way. We've got the address from your subscription — no action needed. Just keep washing like a bastard.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- MILESTONE BADGE -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 40px 0 40px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#0D3B23;border-radius:4px;padding:22px 28px;">
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:#C4733A;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;font-weight:700;">Milestone Unlocked</p>
                        <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#F5EFE6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">{{ event.cycle_count }} Cycles Complete ✓</p>
                      </td>
                      <td align="right" style="font-size:36px;padding-left:16px;">🏆</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:36px 40px 0 40px;text-align:center;">
            <a href="{{ event.rewards_page_url }}?utm_source=klaviyo&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=bastard-club-reward-earned&utm_content=cta" style="display:inline-block;background:#C4733A;color:#0D3B23;padding:16px 44px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;">View Your Rewards →</a>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- DIVIDER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:44px 40px 0 40px;">
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #DDD5C8;font-size:0;">&nbsp;</td></tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- WHATS NEXT -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px 40px 0 40px;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C4733A;">Don't Stop Now.</p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#A09080;">Here's what's coming if you keep washing.</p>

            {% if event.cycle_count >= 20 %}
            <!-- MAXED OUT — all milestones earned -->
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#0D3B23;border-radius:4px;padding:22px 28px;text-align:center;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#C4733A;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;">Legend Status.</p>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.7);line-height:1.6;">You've unlocked everything. 20+ cycles in. That's rare. You're one of the ones who actually stayed the course.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            {% endif %}

            {% if event.cycle_count < 10 %}
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:4px;padding:18px 20px;border-left:3px solid #C4733A;">
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td width="44" style="font-size:32px;vertical-align:middle;">👕</td>
                      <td style="padding-left:14px;vertical-align:middle;">
                        <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#0D3B23;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Free Dirty Bastard Tee</p>
                        <p style="margin:4px 0 0 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#A09080;">{{ 10 | minus: event.cycle_count }} more cycle{% if event.cycle_count == 9 %}{% else %}s{% endif %}. Don't quit.</p>
                      </td>
                      <td align="right" style="font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#C4733A;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:middle;letter-spacing:1px;">10 CYCLES</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            {% endif %}

            {% if event.cycle_count < 20 %}
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:4px;padding:18px 20px;border-left:3px solid #0D3B23;">
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td width="44" style="font-size:32px;vertical-align:middle;">🎁</td>
                      <td style="padding-left:14px;vertical-align:middle;">
                        <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#0D3B23;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">The Legend Pack</p>
                        <p style="margin:4px 0 0 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#A09080;">Tee, hat, mystery gift. {{ 20 | minus: event.cycle_count }} more cycle{% if event.cycle_count == 19 %}{% else %}s{% endif %}.</p>
                      </td>
                      <td align="right" style="font-family:'Oswald','Impact','Arial Black',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#C4733A;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:middle;letter-spacing:1px;">20 CYCLES</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            {% endif %}

          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- SIGN OFF -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:36px 40px 44px 40px;">
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4A3C30;line-height:1.8;">Keep washing.<br><strong style="color:#0D3B23;">— Dirty Bastard</strong></p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#0A2415;padding:32px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.45);">Questions? <a href="mailto:hello@getdirtybastard.com" style="color:#C4733A;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">hello@getdirtybastard.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.25);">Dirty Bastard Laundry Co. · <a href="https://getdirtybastard.com?utm_source=klaviyo&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=bastard-club-reward-earned" style="color:rgba(245,239,230,0.25);text-decoration:none;">getdirtybastard.com</a></p>
            <!-- CAN-SPAM: physical mailing address required. Replace with your PO Box or registered address. -->
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);">715 W Orient St · Tampa, FL</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Barlow',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);">You're receiving this because you give a sheet. <a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}" style="color:rgba(245,239,230,0.18);text-decoration:underline;">Unsubscribe</a></p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
